itunes:title: The Crew and the Surprising Maserati (Matt, Zack, Vinny)
itunes:author: Matt Farah & Zack Klapman
itunes:summary: We went and drove the Maserati Levante Trofeo in the canyons and discovered we had a lot to say about it. We actually filmed a 23-minute review, so there's a lot to discuss. Vinny used to work for Maserati so he helps us understand the Levante. We also talk about the Cayenne comparison, car news, driving, and answer your questions.
